              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter>
                <html:p>Given a type <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[K]]></fr:tex> and a family of <fr:link href="/jms-003O/" title="Reflection algebras and homomorphisms" uri="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-003O/" display-uri="jms-003O" type="local">reflection algebras</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[X : K\to  {A}\downarrow {\mathcal {U}}]]></fr:tex> such that the dependent product <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{{\mathopen {}\left (k:K\right )\mathclose {}}}}{\textstyle \prod _{{\mathopen {}\left (k:K\right )\mathclose {}}}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{{\mathopen {}\left (k:K\right )\mathclose {}}}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{{\mathopen {}\left (k:K\right )\mathclose {}}}}U{\mathopen {}\left (Xk\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> lies in <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {U}]]></fr:tex>, we may define the product of product of <fr:link href="/jms-003O/" title="Reflection algebras and homomorphisms" uri="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-003O/" display-uri="jms-003O" type="local">reflection algebras</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{{\mathopen {}\left (k:K\right )\mathclose {}}}}{\textstyle \prod _{{\mathopen {}\left (k:K\right )\mathclose {}}}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{{\mathopen {}\left (k:K\right )\mathclose {}}}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{{\mathopen {}\left (k:K\right )\mathclose {}}}}Xk]]></fr:tex> to have the following structure map:</html:p>
                <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[  \begin {array}{l}
  \eta _{\mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{{\mathopen {}\left (k:K\right )\mathclose {}}}}{\textstyle \prod _{{\mathopen {}\left (k:K\right )\mathclose {}}}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{{\mathopen {}\left (k:K\right )\mathclose {}}}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{{\mathopen {}\left (k:K\right )\mathclose {}}}}Xk} : A \to  \mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{{\mathopen {}\left (k:K\right )\mathclose {}}}}{\textstyle \prod _{{\mathopen {}\left (k:K\right )\mathclose {}}}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{{\mathopen {}\left (k:K\right )\mathclose {}}}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{{\mathopen {}\left (k:K\right )\mathclose {}}}}{Xk} \\
